UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2205
1 WHEREAS, the Commonwealth of Kentucky recognizes the importance of finding
2 the cause and cures for MS and expresses its appreciation for the dedication that the
3 National Multiple Sclerosis Society Kentucky-Tennessee Chapter has shown toward
4 creating a world free of MS;
5 NOW, THEREFORE,
6 Be it resolved by the House of Representatives of the General Assembly of the
7 Commonwealth of Kentucky:
8 Section 1. The House of Representatives does hereby recognize March 8 to 14,
9 2026, as Multiple Sclerosis Awareness Week in Kentucky.
10 Section 2. The Clerk of the House of Representatives is directed to transmit a
11 copy of this Resolution to Representative Erika Hancock for delivery.
